#: ../../source/janim/components/glow.rst:2
msgid "glow"
msgstr "glow"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow:1 of
msgid "泛光组件"
msgstr "Glow component"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow.set:1 of
msgid "``color`` 表示传入的 ``RGB`` 颜色数据，单个颜色 （支持 ``'#FF0000'`` ``'red'`` ``[1, 0, 0.5]`` 的表示）"
msgstr ""
"``color`` represents the ``RGB`` color data passed in, a single color (supports formats like ``'#FF0000'``, ``'red'``, "
"``[1, 0, 0.5]``)"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow.set:3 of
msgid "``alpha`` 表示传入的透明度数据 （``1`` 表示不透明，``0`` 表示完全透明）"
msgstr "``alpha`` represents the transparency data passed in (``1`` means opaque, ``0`` means fully transparent)"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow.set:5 of
msgid "``size`` 表示泛光的大小"
msgstr "``size`` represents the size of the glow"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow.set:6 of
msgid "默认情况下会将所有后代物件也设置成指定的属性，传入 ``root_only=True`` 可以只设置根物件的"
msgstr ""
"By default, all descendant items will also be set to the specified properties; passing ``root_only=True`` will only set "
"the root item's properties"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow.set:8 of
msgid "特殊传参："
msgstr "Special parameter passing:"

#: janim.components.glow.Cmpt_Glow.set:10 of
msgid "当 ``color`` 为四分量 ``RGBA`` 颜色数据时， 则同时表示了 ``color`` 和 ``alpha`` 二者，因此不能再传入 ``alpha`` 参数"
msgstr ""
"When ``color`` is four-component ``RGBA`` color data, it represents both ``color`` and ``alpha``, so the ``alpha`` "
"parameter cannot be passed separately"
